# .clang-format - Matches STYLEGUIDE.md

BasedOnStyle: LLVM
IndentWidth: 4
UseTab: Never
ColumnLimit: 100
AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: false
DerivePointerAlignment: false
PointerAlignment: Left
BreakBeforeBraces: Attach
BraceWrapping:
  AfterClass: false
  AfterFunction: false
  AfterNamespace: false
  AfterEnum: false
  AfterStruct: false
  AfterUnion: false
  BeforeCatch: false
  BeforeElse: false
SpacesInAngles: false
SpaceAfterCStyleCast: true
AlwaysBreakTemplateDeclarations: Yes
SortIncludes: true
IncludeBlocks: Preserve
AlignConsecutiveAssignments: true
AlignConsecutiveDeclarations: true
AlignOperands: true

# Notes:
# - 4 spaces everywhere.
# - K&R style braces ("Attach" = same line).
# - Limit columns to 100 for readability.
# - Left-aligned * and & for pointers/references.
# - Group consecutive assignments nicely aligned.
# - Sort includes but preserve logical include blocks.
# - Break long templates for better clarity.
